jasperReport.name: BB_Data_Tapes
jasperReport.queryString:
SELECT 'Existing Data Tape' as Group_Tape ,RefMon ,`Loan ID` ,`First Name` ,`Last Name` ,`Borrower Name` ,`Date of Birth` ,`Address` ,`City` ,`Zip Code` ,`Province` ,`Business_Unit` ,`Product Type` ,`Store Name` ,`Merchant_Store_ID` ,`Date of Loan` ,`Insurance_Flag` ,`Original Term (Days)` ,`Original Rate` ,`Loan_Amount` ,`Finance_Charge` ,`Fee_Charge` ,`Principal_Paid` ,`FinCharge_Paid` ,`FeeCharge_Paid` ,`Total Amount Paid` ,`Cumulative Principal_Paid` ,`Cumulative FinCharge_Paid` ,`Cumulative FeeCharge_Paid` ,`Current Principal Balance` ,`Interest_Balance` ,`Fee_Balance` ,`Current Total Balance` ,`LastPmtDate` ,`Days since last payment` ,`Days Delinquent` ,`Delinquency Status` ,cast(case when `Bureau Score` = 'NA' then 0 else `Bureau Score` end as signed) as `Bureau Score` ,`Loan_Type` ,`Cust_Tenure (Months)` ,`FL_BKY` ,`FL_Eligibility` ,`FL_NotInNew` ,`Type 1 Delinquency` ,`Type 2 Delinquency` ,`Type 3 Delinquency` ,`Meets all qualitative Eligibility Criteria` ,`Less than max UPB at Origination` ,`Meets Minimum Interest Payments` ,`Eligible Loan Type` ,`Eligible` ,`Eligible Receivable Balance` ,`Eligible Receivable Balance (w/Score)`
FROM mogodb03.FortressBB_Hist WHERE RefMon = $P{CurrFundDate} AND `Product Type` NOT IN ('Pocket Money', 'Zip Advance') AND `Loan Id` IN (SELECT `Loan Id` FROM mogodb03.FortressBB_Hist WHERE RefMon = $P{PrevFundDate})
UNION
SELECT 'New Data Tape' as Group_Tape ,RefMon ,`Loan ID` ,`First Name` ,`Last Name` ,`Borrower Name` ,`Date of Birth` ,`Address` ,`City` ,`Zip Code` ,`Province` ,`Business_Unit` ,`Product Type` ,`Store Name` ,`Merchant_Store_ID` ,`Date of Loan` ,`Insurance_Flag` ,`Original Term (Days)` ,`Original Rate` ,`Loan_Amount` ,`Finance_Charge` ,`Fee_Charge` ,`Principal_Paid` ,`FinCharge_Paid` ,`FeeCharge_Paid` ,`Total Amount Paid` ,`Cumulative Principal_Paid` ,`Cumulative FinCharge_Paid` ,`Cumulative FeeCharge_Paid` ,`Current Principal Balance` ,`Interest_Balance` ,`Fee_Balance` ,`Current Total Balance` ,`LastPmtDate` ,`Days since last payment` ,`Days Delinquent` ,`Delinquency Status` ,cast(case when `Bureau Score` = 'NA' then 0 else `Bureau Score` end as signed) as `Bureau Score` ,`Loan_Type` ,`Cust_Tenure (Months)` ,`FL_BKY` ,`FL_Eligibility` ,`FL_NotInNew` ,`Type 1 Delinquency` ,`Type 2 Delinquency` ,`Type 3 Delinquency` ,`Meets all qualitative Eligibility Criteria` ,`Less than max UPB at Origination` ,`Meets Minimum Interest Payments` ,`Eligible Loan Type` ,`Eligible` ,`Eligible Receivable Balance` ,`Eligible Receivable Balance (w/Score)`
FROM mogodb03.FortressBB_Hist WHERE RefMon = $P{CurrFundDate} AND `Product Type` NOT IN ('Pocket Money', 'Zip Advance') AND `Loan Id` NOT IN (SELECT `Loan Id` FROM mogodb03.FortressBB_Hist WHERE RefMon = $P{PrevFundDate})
